Package: llamaR
Title: CLI-First AI Agent Runtime for R Built on MCP
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Troy", "Hernandez", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "troy@cornball.ai")
Description: An interactive CLI agent that connects to LLMs (Anthropic, OpenAI,
    Ollama) and gives them direct access to a live R session via the Model
    Context Protocol (MCP). Provides both an MCP server exposing R-native tools
    and a CLI agent for terminal-based AI workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/cornball-ai/llamaR
BugReports: https://github.com/cornball-ai/llamaR/issues
Imports:
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    llm.api,
    tinytest
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
